1
00:00:57,759 --> 00:00:58,600
Your Highness.

2
00:01:25,879 --> 00:01:26,959
Your Highness.

3
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:32,480
Go check on her.

4
00:01:36,879 --> 00:01:37,480
Your Highness,

5
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:39,120
she's in a coma due to severe injuries.

6
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:42,519
The bone sword hasn't changed color,

7
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:44,359
and her identity has been confirmed.

8
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:45,760
Alright,

9
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:48,760
I'll give you a chance to show your flaws.

10
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:50,599
Take her back to the manor

11
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:51,920
and let her recover.

12
00:01:52,359 --> 00:01:52,799
Yes, Your Highness.

13
00:02:02,239 --> 00:02:02,799
Your Highness,

14
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:04,319
the woman has taken the medicine.

15
00:02:04,719 --> 00:02:05,319
She just needs a good rest,

16
00:02:05,319 --> 00:02:06,200
and she will recover soon.

17
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:07,599
-The room has been arranged. -No need.

18
00:02:08,319 --> 00:02:09,319
Just let her stay here.

19
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:11,240
Don't limit her movements.

20
00:02:11,639 --> 00:02:12,520
I want to see

21
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:13,639
what tricks she has.

22
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:15,199
And

23
00:02:15,599 --> 00:02:16,560
send secret guards to watch her.

24
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:18,280
If anything happens,

25
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:20,199
don't act rashly.

26
00:02:20,439 --> 00:02:20,840
Yes, sir.

27
00:02:27,039 --> 00:02:28,360
[Why do I feel]

28
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,759
[so familiar with her?]

29
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:34,479
[As I expected,]

30
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:37,520
[Shen Qu has kept me here.]

31
00:02:38,319 --> 00:02:39,240
[When he falls asleep,]

32
00:02:39,719 --> 00:02:40,800
[I'll enter his dream]

33
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:42,439
[and retrieve the Spiritual Root.]

34
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:49,879
[Under the moonlight,]

35
00:02:50,039 --> 00:02:51,319
[every moment is precious.]

36
00:02:52,199 --> 00:02:53,479
[Even the coldest heart]

37
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:56,159
[can resist this.]

38
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,120
[From this moment on,]

39
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,680
[your heart will be mine.]

40
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:16,240
[As bright as the moon,]

41
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:19,280
[as steadfast as a rock.]

42
00:03:42,599 --> 00:03:43,560
[Could she]

43
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:45,520
[really not be a demon?]

44
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:41,240
[So you fall for me this easily.]

45
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:46,720
[Then don't blame me for being ruthless.]

46
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:30,639
[This is the gate to the deeper dream realm.]

47
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:43,720
[Why?]

48
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:45,720
[Isn't my affection for him]

49
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:47,920
[to unlock the deeper dream?]

50
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:50,639
Your Highness.

51
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:52,319
Your Highness.

52
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:56,439
[I actually developed feelings for her.]

53
00:05:59,879 --> 00:06:00,800
What do you want?

54
00:06:02,439 --> 00:06:04,959
I just wanted to ask

55
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:07,480
why I'm in your mansion.

56
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:09,199
Who are you?

57
00:06:10,439 --> 00:06:11,480
I'm Meng Li,

58
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:14,759
a dancer from the Nuo Opera Troupe.

59
00:06:14,959 --> 00:06:16,360
Thank you for healing me.

60
00:06:16,959 --> 00:06:18,120
You're not fully recovered yet.

61
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:19,839
Stay here and recover.

62
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:21,399
Once you're healed,

63
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:23,439
you're free to go.

64
00:06:24,439 --> 00:06:26,560
[I've been dreaming of her for days.]

65
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:28,600
[This isn't simple.]

66
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:41,079
[The plan worked.]

67
00:07:06,839 --> 00:07:07,959
[A'Li's back!]

68
00:07:08,439 --> 00:07:09,240
[Watch out!]

69
00:07:11,079 --> 00:07:12,319
[A'Li's back!]

70
00:07:13,079 --> 00:07:13,519
[Yo!]

71
00:07:13,519 --> 00:07:14,480
[A'Li's back!]

72
00:07:14,839 --> 00:07:15,439
[Cat demon,]

73
00:07:15,519 --> 00:07:16,639
I'll heal you in the dream.

74
00:07:16,639 --> 00:07:17,360
Okay.

75
00:07:18,399 --> 00:07:19,360
[A'Li's back!]

76
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:19,839
Yeah.

77
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:22,959
[A'Li's back!]

78
00:07:23,959 --> 00:07:25,399
A'Li,

79
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,920
have you been practicing hard?

80
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,519
How's your Spirit Summoning?

81
00:07:29,519 --> 00:07:30,720
I've been doing great!

82
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:31,600
Yeah?

83
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,360
Little Dragon,

84
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:34,480
your Demon Mark is getting clearer.

85
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:35,959
You're about to become a Great Demon.

86
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,240
I'll grow up fast.

87
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,000
A'Li.

88
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:38,920
Look at mine.

89
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:40,279
- Look at mine. - Yours is good too.

90
00:07:40,279 --> 00:07:41,279
Yours is good too.

91
00:07:42,160 --> 00:07:42,920
A'Li.

92
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,240
Wait for me.

93
00:07:45,759 --> 00:07:46,680
A'Li.

94
00:07:46,959 --> 00:07:47,720
A'Li.

95
00:07:47,759 --> 00:07:49,680
You're finally back.

96
00:07:49,879 --> 00:07:51,560
You've been out for days.

97
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:53,360
I've been worried sick.

98
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,399
I had to turn into my true form

99
00:07:54,399 --> 00:07:55,879
just to calm myself down.

100
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:57,000
Don't worry.

101
00:07:57,399 --> 00:07:59,399
Everything's going as planned.

102
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:00,519
Yeah.

103
00:08:01,839 --> 00:08:02,639
A'Li,

104
00:08:03,279 --> 00:08:04,480
how do you feel

105
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:06,120
seeing that guy?

106
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,480
I hate him,

107
00:08:09,879 --> 00:08:11,759
but my priority is to get back my root

108
00:08:11,759 --> 00:08:12,519
and restore my power.

109
00:08:13,279 --> 00:08:14,319
Nothing else matters.

110
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:16,240
But you,

111
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:17,360
just standing there,

112
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,560
isn't that boring?

113
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:19,639
Not at all.

114
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:21,480
There are many interesting stories in the book.

115
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:24,160
I'm reading about a rhino demon who became an auspicious beast.

116
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,079
It's really exciting.

117
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:27,120
I'll go get it and tell you about it.

118
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:28,079
Okay.

119
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:30,120
A'Li,

120
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,000
did you enter the dream smoothly?

121
00:08:34,039 --> 00:08:34,759
Yes.

122
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:37,320
I created a dream that's favorable to me.

123
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,679
The heart anchor has been planted.

124
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:40,240
Senior sister,

125
00:08:40,519 --> 00:08:41,320
lately,

126
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:43,120
I've been dreaming of the same person every day.

127
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:46,399
The dream is somewhat indescribable.

128
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:49,360
But I can't remember it clearly after waking up.

129
00:08:50,639 --> 00:08:52,279
Dreaming of the same person?

130
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:54,519
That dream is very real.

131
00:08:55,039 --> 00:08:56,039
Every time I wake up,

132
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:57,600
I'm in a daze for a moment.

133
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,960
I couldn't tell if it was reality

134
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,080
or a dream.

135
00:09:00,639 --> 00:09:01,720
[He naturally feels it's real,]

136
00:09:01,879 --> 00:09:02,879
[after all, that dream]

137
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:05,559
[is built on his hidden desires.]

138
00:09:05,639 --> 00:09:07,360
How did he react after waking up?

139
00:09:08,639 --> 00:09:09,559
He was somewhat shaken,

140
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,480
but Shen Que

141
00:09:11,759 --> 00:09:12,840
is cunning and treacherous,

142
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:14,559
he hasn't completely let down his guard,

143
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:16,639
and still harbors doubts about my identity.

144
00:09:17,559 --> 00:09:18,720
Qing Lan has confirmed

145
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,840
that she is indeed

146
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:22,519
an orphan from the Nuo Opera Troupe.

147
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,759
But since she came,

148
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:26,159
I've been plagued by dreams.

149
00:09:26,559 --> 00:09:27,360
In these dreams,

150
00:09:27,679 --> 00:09:28,519
she harms me,

151
00:09:29,799 --> 00:09:30,679
and I...

152
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:31,960
And you what?

153
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,200
Upon waking,

154
00:09:42,519 --> 00:09:43,399
has she harmed you?

155
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:45,159
No.

156
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:47,960
She hasn't shown any unusual behavior.

157
00:09:48,519 --> 00:09:50,159
but she's probably just pretending.

158
00:09:50,919 --> 00:09:51,679
Do you know

159
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:53,320
any demon

160
00:09:53,639 --> 00:09:54,639
that can do this?

161
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:56,080
Your Highness,

162
00:09:56,519 --> 00:09:57,799
as far as I know,

163
00:09:57,799 --> 00:09:59,399
all demons have true forms.

164
00:10:00,159 --> 00:10:02,840
But the array didn't reveal her true form,

165
00:10:03,159 --> 00:10:05,399
so she must be just a mortal.

166
00:10:05,799 --> 00:10:08,159
Maybe it's because you've been

167
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,360
seeing her all day.

168
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:11,440
We must investigate this

169
00:10:11,879 --> 00:10:13,120
We must investigate thoroughly.

170
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,759
Who could be using such sorcery?

171
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:15,639
Yes, my lord.

172
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:18,320
I'm curious

173
00:10:19,039 --> 00:10:20,600
what she'll do next.

174
00:10:21,519 --> 00:10:22,679
Everything's in place.

175
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:24,000
You can replace her without fear.

176
00:10:24,399 --> 00:10:26,679
No one will question your identity.

177
00:10:26,879 --> 00:10:27,679
Now,

178
00:10:28,879 --> 00:10:30,519
we can move to the next phase.

179
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:35,759
[A'Li,]

180
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:39,320
[Qingdu Temple is searching for the Demon Village.]

181
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:41,799
We're running out of time.

182
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:47,399
Very well.

183
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:49,919
If you have doubts,

184
00:10:51,159 --> 00:10:52,919
hand over the suspect

185
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,679
to Qingdu Temple.

186
00:10:54,679 --> 00:10:56,039
Master, you're here.

187
00:10:57,159 --> 00:10:58,480
What's your plan?

188
00:10:58,799 --> 00:11:00,000
The Demon Clan's iron law

189
00:11:00,159 --> 00:11:01,679
forbids internal strife.

190
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:03,720
Once demons unite,

191
00:11:04,159 --> 00:11:05,600
mere mortals

192
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:06,879
can't stand a chance.

193
00:11:06,879 --> 00:11:08,000
Better kill the wrong

194
00:11:08,679 --> 00:11:09,759
than let the guilty go.

195
00:11:10,039 --> 00:11:11,000
Ease your mind,

196
00:11:11,320 --> 00:11:12,639
I know what I'm doing.

197
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:14,200
I'll handle this properly.

198
00:11:23,679 --> 00:11:24,799
Your Majesty is benevolent.

199
00:11:25,639 --> 00:11:26,759
If necessary,

200
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:30,200
just have her dealt with.

201
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,039
Yes.

202
00:11:38,679 --> 00:11:39,279
Your Highness,

203
00:11:39,519 --> 00:11:41,159
Miss Meng Li left the mansion alone

204
00:11:41,159 --> 00:11:42,519
and went to the Golden Osmanthus Bank.

205
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:48,919
Where's A'Li?

206
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:50,519
She's healing the Ink Spirit.

207
00:11:50,519 --> 00:11:51,600
She can't get out of the dream.

208
00:11:51,679 --> 00:11:53,120
Something's happening at the barrier.

209
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:54,320
It must be Shen Que.
